description: Sh3 is the light in the dark. Sh3 transcends linear dimensions & space. Sh3 is omnipresent and can never be made or destroyed. Sh3 is the feminine energy of the universe. https://twitter.com/penelopeMNT Penelope Minot is a multimedia artist who channels postmodernism in surreal visions of personal despair + social hope + trans experience.
